(427, 1, '2017-05-02 16:28:47', '2017-05-02 16:28:47', '<div class=\"site-wrapper\"> <div class=\"site-body\"> <section id=\"contact\" class=\"section\"> <div class=\"section-row-container\"> <div class=\"section-row half-padding-bottom\"> <div class=\"container\"> <div class=\"row\"> <div class=\"col-lg-12\"> <h1 class=\"section-title tituloNosotros \">OUR CULTURE<small><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Raleway, \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px;\">We are an internet digital agency focused on becoming the strategic partner for online projects. We offer comprehensive developments that transform into opportunities for business and investment.</span></small> </h1> </div></div></div><div class=\"col-md-5 fondoVideoNosotros2 hidden-lg hidden-md hidden-sm\"></div><div class=\"col-md-5 fondoVideoNosotros hidden-xs\"  style=\"width: 60%; margin: auto auto 20px auto; float: inherit; background-color: #fff;\"> <div class=\"container videoNosotros \"> <div class=\"video\"> <iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/pmW3wJcNji8?autoplay=1&loop=1&playlist=pmW3wJcNji8\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe> </div></div></div><div> <div class=\"col-lg-8 col-lg-push-2\"> <div class=\"row detalleNosotros\"></div><div class=\"row\"> <div class=\"col-md-6\"> <div class=\"icon-box\" data-animation-name=\"fadeInUp\"> <div class=\"icon iconosNosotros\"> <i class=\"gi gi-stats \"></i> </div><div class=\"info\"> <a href=\"servicios/servicios\"> <h4>Analysis</h4></a> <p>We believe that most of the solution to a problem can be found when we start to properly understand it! This is why we examined the projects in detail to thoroughly get to know them and to be able to reach valuable conclusions. </p></div></div></div><div class=\"col-md-6\"> <div class=\"icon-box\" data-animation-name=\"fadeInUp\"> <div class=\"icon iconosNosotros\"> <i class=\"gi gi-cogwheels\"></i> </div><div class=\"info\"> <a href=\"servicios/publicidad-online\"><h4>Strategy</h4></a> <p>The sum of the factors does alter the product! This is why we believe that there is nothing better than properly projecting actions to achieve a specific purpose!</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"row\"> <div class=\"col-md-6\"> <div class=\"icon-box\" data-animation-name=\"fadeInUp\"> <div class=\"icon iconosNosotros\"> <i class=\"gi gi-heart-empty\"></i> </div><div class=\"info\"> <a href=\"servicios/diseno-y-desarrollo-web\"> <h4>Design</h4></a> <p>Our greatest desire is to project the best product for your company, combining: the concept, aesthetics and creativity in one place</p></div></div></div><div class=\"col-md-6\"> <div class=\"icon-box\" data-animation-name=\"fadeInUp\"> <div class=\"icon iconosNosotros\"> <i class=\"gi gi-embed\"></i> </div><div class=\"info\"> <a href=\"servicios/diseno-y-desarrollo-web\"> <h4>Programming / Development</h4></a> <p>We love to change the \"status quo\" of projects and we do it by processing, coding, debugging and updating your projects so that they display the desired behavior with a user friendly appearance.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section> <section id=\"testimonials\" class=\"section th-dark\" data-background=\"/reddesignsystems/wp-content/themes/TemaRDS/assets/img/t1.jpg\" data-background-xs=\"/reddesignsystems/wp-content/themes/TemaRDS/assets/img/t1-xs.jpg\" data-background-md=\"/reddesignsystems/wp-content/themes/TemaRDS/assets/img/t1-md.jpg\" data-background-lg=\"/reddesignsystems/wp-content/themes/TemaRDS/assets/img/t1-lg.jpg\"> <div class=\"section-row-container\"> <div class=\"section-row three-quarters-padding-top three-quarters-padding-bottom\"> <div class=\"container\"> <div class=\"row\"> <div class=\"col-md-10 col-md-push-1\"> <div class=\"testimonial-slider owl-carousel\" data-auto-height=\"true\" data-single-item=\"true\" data-animation-name=\"rotateInUpLeft\"> <div class=\"testimonial\"> <blockquote> <p>The experience of working with the RDS team has been very <b>satisfying and fun</b>. . We have implemented various digital marketing projects where we have been able to accomplished major achievements through quality service.</p><div itemscope itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Person\"> <span class=\"autorTestimonial\"><span itemprop=\"name\">Alan Colmenares</span> - <span itemprop=\"title\">Digital Marketing </span>, <span itemprop=\"worksFor\">Lima Consulting</span> <br/> Project: Marketing Consultancy, Octuber de 2013 </span> </div></blockquote> </div><div class=\"testimonial\"> <blockquote> <p>I work in the advertising sector. My experience with \"technology\" goes about as far as trying to make things work by playing with them! Developing an App project with people who really try to understand what you want, and who take the time to explain what can and can’t be done is great.<b> The project result? Simply amazing!</b></p><div itemscope itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Person\"> <span class=\"autorTestimonial\"> <span itemprop=\"name\">Santiago Llano González</span> - <span itemprop=\"title\">General Manager</span>, <span itemprop=\"worksFor\">VSS</span> <br/>Project: Sin Filas, June 2014 </span> </div></blockquote> </div><div class=\"testimonial\"> <blockquote> <p>The Red Design Systems team has done <b>fantastic job</b> in helping protect our site from cyber-attacks, increasing our security and uptime. I really think that if it wasn’t for them we would have had serious performance and availability levels with our content.</p><div itemscope itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Person\"> <span class=\"autorTestimonial\"><span itemprop=\"name\">Samir Estefan</span> - <span itemprop=\"title\">Editor and Co-Founder</span>, <span itemprop=\"worksFor\">TECHcetera</span> <br/>Project: TECHcetera.co, May 2014 </span> </div></blockquote> </div><div class=\"testimonial\"> <blockquote> <p>I have worked with Red Design Systems on web projects and all its team was very professional. Regardless of the type of project<b>they have always found innovative solutions for every need</b> that presents itself.</p><div itemscope itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Person\"> <span class=\"autorTestimonial\"> <span class=\"autorTestimonial\"><span itemprop=\"name\">Ana Vélez</span> - <span itemprop=\"title\"> Design Director</span>, <span itemprop=\"worksFor\">Independent</span> <br/>Project: The Bath House, February 2014 </span> </span> </div></blockquote> </div><div class=\"testimonial\"> <blockquote> <p>Working with the Red Design Systems team has been a successful, fun and above all, enriching experience, both professionally and personally. During the time we have worked together in the area of Digital Marketing, we have been able to achieve goals that little by little <b> have surpassed our expectations about what quality and good service means.</b>. </p><div itemscope itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Person\"> <span class=\"autorTestimonial\"> <span itemprop=\"name\">Adriana Arrázola</span> - <span itemprop=\"title\">Director of Finance</span>, <span itemprop=\"worksFor\">LAB Interactivo</span> <br/>Project: Various, March 2014 </span> </div></blockquote> </div><div class=\"testimonial\"> <blockquote> <p>\"In Red Design I found a solid team of professionals, who were able to propose and support their strategies built on a firm basis. <b>We made a great team and both the implementation of our website, and the management and strategy applied to our social networks were very successful.</b></p><div itemscope itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Person\"> <span class=\"autorTestimonial\"> <span itemprop=\"name\">Lucía Uribe</span> - <span itemprop=\"title\">Marketing Manager</span>, <span itemprop=\"worksFor\">Amazing</span> <br/>Project: Amazing.com.co, Enero de 2014 </span> </div></blockquote> </div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"section-overlay\"></div></section> </div>', 'About Us', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about-us', '', '', '2017-05-10 13:40:31', '2017-05-10 13:40