(513, 1, '2017-05-08 19:25:15', '2017-05-08 19:25:15', '<div class=\"site-wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"site-body\"><section id=\"contact\" class=\"section\">\r\n<div class=\"section-row-container\">\r\n<div class=\"section-row half-padding-bottom\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12\">\r\n<h1 class=\"section-title tituloNosotros\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px;\">PRIVACY AND INFORMATION</h1>\r\nFor<strong> RDS SAS</strong> the protection and privacy of the personal information of our Clients, Suppliers, Contractors, Collaborators and Followers is very important to us. That is why we have adopted a Privacy Policy that describes the handling and management of the personal information in the databases that we collect due to our activities, ensuring the confidentiality and protection of the data, as described below:\r\n\r\nThe users acknowledge that any inputting of personal information is done on a voluntary basis, meaning that the information will form part of a file and/or database, which can be used in the terms established herein.\r\n\r\nWhoever fills out the registration form agrees that their details will be added to the <strong>RDS SAS</strong> database and those of its affiliates or subsidiaries, and authorizes its use for commercial and technical purposes by <strong>RDS SAS</strong> and its affiliates, including but not limited to its partners, business partners, customers and advertisers.\r\n\r\nUsers may modify or update the information provided at any time and may request the removal of their personal information in the databases of RDS SAS by emailing <a href=\"mailto:contacto@reddesignsystems.com\">contacto@reddesignsystems.com</a>. The removal of information from the databases may mean the loss of the privileges derived from registration.\r\n\r\nUsers who have access keys to the Website or Associated Resources, understand that their use is personal and non-transferable and they must properly and responsibly use their passwords, as it is their sole responsibility.\r\n\r\n<strong>RDS SAS </strong>is committed to fulfilling its obligation surrounding the confidentiality of personal data and assumes, for these purposes, the technical, organizational and security measures necessary to prevent its alteration, loss, or unauthorized access in accordance with the provisions of current Colombian law. Bearing in mind that no Internet transmission is 100% secure, users hereby acknowledge and assume the hypothetical risk inherent in this type of transmission.\r\n\r\n<strong>RDS SAS</strong> is not responsible for any consequence resulting from the improper admission of third parties to the database and/or for any technical malfunction and/or retention of data in the Website system or its Associated Resources.\r\n\r\nThe companies that manage advertising for RDS SAS, advertisers, or companies who have access to statistics may use cookies for statistical purposes. Users can eliminate or prevent the use of cookies from their browser options installed on their respective computer equipment.\r\n\r\nUsers must comply with the Terms and Conditions of Site and any additional conditions specified in the Website or in the Associated Resources.\r\n\r\nThese Terms and Conditions have been prepared in accordance with Colombian law and any action or claim must be made before the courts of Colombia.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section></div>\r\n</div>', 'Privacy and information', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'privacy-and-information', '', '', '2017-05-08 19:38:49', '2017-05-08 19:38:49', '', 0, 'http://172.16.7.177/reddesignsystems/?page_id=513', 0, 'page', '', 0),
