to the 8th NOC Forum to: find their way around the forum easily through augmented reality, visualize meeting and event agendas online, get complementary information on art expositions and a lot more. </p>\r\n											<h5 class=\"tituloTagsVideoGaleria\">Tags</h5> \r\n											<span class=\"tagsVideoGaleria\">mobile development, </span> \r\n										</div>\r\n									</div>\r\n									<!--======================================Video==================================================-->\r\n								\r\n								</div>\r\n							</div>\r\n						</div>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</section> \r\n	</div>\r\n</div>', 'Videos', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'videos', '', '', '2017-05-08 19:13:42', '2017-05-08 19:13:42', '', 0, 'http://172.16.7.177/reddesignsystems/?page_id=541', 0, 'page', '', 0),
