ect<b>they have always found innovative solutions for every need</b> that presents itself.</p><div itemscope itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Person\"> <span class=\"autorTestimonial\"> <span class=\"autorTestimonial\"><span itemprop=\"name\">Ana Vélez</span> - <span itemprop=\"title\"> Design Director</span>, <span itemprop=\"worksFor\">Independent</span> <br/>Project: The Bath House, February 2014 </span> </span> </div></blockquote> </div><div class=\"testimonial\"> <blockquote> <p>Working with the Red Design Systems team has been a successful, fun and above all, enriching experience, both professionally and personally. During the time we have worked together in the area of Digital Marketing, we have been able to achieve goals that little by little <b> have surpassed our expectations about what quality and good service means.</b>. </p><div itemscope itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Person\"> <span class=\"autorTestimonial\"> <span itemprop=\"name\">Adriana Arrázola</span> - <span itemprop=\"title\">Director of Finance</span>, <span itemprop=\"worksFor\">LAB Interactivo</span> <br/>Project: Various, March 2014 </span> </div></blockquote> </div><div class=\"testimonial\"> <blockquote> <p>\"In Red Design I found a solid team of professionals, who were able to propose and support their strategies built on a firm basis. <b>We made a great team and both the implementation of our website, and the management and strategy applied to our social networks were very successful.</b></p><div itemscope itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Person\"> <span class=\"autorTestimonial\"> <span itemprop=\"name\">Lucía Uribe</span> - <span itemprop=\"title\">Marketing Manager</span>, <span itemprop=\"worksFor\">Amazing</span> <br/>Project: Amazing.com.co, Enero de 2014 </span> </div></blockquote> </div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"section-overlay\"></div></section> </div>', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '427-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-05-10 13:34:21', '2017-05-1