g with the RDS team has been very <b>satisfying and fun</b>. . We have implemented various digital marketing projects where we have been able to accomplished major achievements through quality service.</p><div itemscope itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Person\"> <span class=\"autorTestimonial\"><span itemprop=\"name\">Alan Colmenares</span> - <span itemprop=\"title\">Digital Marketing </span>, <span itemprop=\"worksFor\">Lima Consulting</span> <br/> Project: Marketing Consultancy, Octuber de 2013 </span> </div></blockquote> </div><div class=\"testimonial\"> <blockquote> <p>I work in the advertising sector. My experience with \"technology\" goes about as far as trying to make things work by playing with them! Developing an App project with people who really try to understand what you want, and who take the time to explain what can and can’t be done is great.<b> The project result? Simply amazing!</b></p><div itemscope itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Person\"> <span class=\"autorTestimonial\"> <span itemprop=\"name\">Santiago Llano González</span> - <span itemprop=\"title\">General Manager</span>, <span itemprop=\"worksFor\">VSS</span> <br/>Project: Sin Filas, June 2014 </span> </div></blockquote> </div><div class=\"testimonial\"> <blockquote> <p>The Red Design Systems team has done <b>fantastic job</b> in helping protect our site from cyber-attacks, increasing our security and uptime. I really think that if it wasn’t for them we would have had serious performance and availability levels with our content.</p><div itemscope itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Person\"> <span class=\"autorTestimonial\"><span itemprop=\"name\">Samir Estefan</span> - <span itemprop=\"title\">Editor and Co-Founder</span>, <span itemprop=\"worksFor\">TECHcetera</span> <br/>Project: TECHcetera.co, May 2014 </span> </div></blockquote> </div><div class=\"testimonial\"> <blockquote> <p>I have worked with Red Design Systems on web projects and all its team was very professional. Regardless of the type of project<b>they have always found innovative solutions for every need</b> that presents itself.</p><div itemscope itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Person\"> <span class=\"autorTestimonial\"> <span class=\"autorTestimonial\"><span itemprop=\"name\">Ana Vélez</span> - <span itemprop=\"title\"> Design Director</span>, <span itemprop=\"worksFor\">Independent</span> <br/>Project: The Bath House, February 2014 </span> </span> </div></blockquote> </div><div class=\"testimonial\"> <blockquote> <p>Working with the Red Design Systems team has been a successful, fun and above all, enriching experience, both professionally and personally. During the time we have worked together in the area of Digital Marketing, we have been able to achieve goals that little by little <b> have surpassed our expectations about what quality and good service means.</b>. </p><div itemscope itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Person\"> <span class=\"autorTestimonial\"> <span itemprop=\"name\">Adriana Arrázola</span> - <span itemprop=\"title\">Directora of Finance</span>, <span itemprop=\"worksFor\">LAB Interactivo</span> <br/>Project: Various, March 2014 </span> </div></blockquote> </div><div class=\"testimonial\"> <blockquote> <p>En Red Design Systems encontré <strong> un equipo sólido, capaz de proponer y sustentar con fundamento sus estrategias.</strong> <br/>Hicimos un gran equipo y tanto la implementación de nuestro sitio web, como la gestión y estrategia aplicada a nuestras redes sociales, fueron exitosas.</p><div itemscope itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Person\"> <span class=\"autorTestimonial\"> <span itemprop=\"name\">Lucía Uribe</span> - <span itemprop=\"title\">Gerente de Mercadeo</span>, <span itemprop=\"worksFor\">Amazing</span> <br/>Proyecto: Amazing.com.co, Enero de 2014 </span> </div></blockquote> </div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"section-overlay\"></div></section> </div>', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '427-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-05-10 13:28:47', '2017-05