(731, 1, '2017-05-10 19:54:00', '2017-05-10 19:54:00', '<strong>Website Development, Redesign and support</strong>\r\nWeb design and implementation of a web content management system (CMS) for generating, editing and updating news. TECHcetera quickly became one of the best known news and information sites on technology in Colombia. The website was redesigned to adapt to the demands of the market and to strengthen the scope of the project.\r\n\r\nAnother customer requirement, which arose during development, was to provide continuous support for the page to ensure continuous uptime, despite the continuing attacks by malicious hackers.\r\n\r\n<strong>Tech Support</strong>\r\nOur goal is to become strategic partners to ensure the growth of our clients.\r\n\r\nThanks to our consulting services and support in developing strategies and campaigns for Internet advertising, TECHcetera has managed to achieve a huge volume of Interaction and traffic within its niche, representing an invaluable potential for the project and its future profitability.\r\n<a href=\"http://www.techcetera.co/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Link</a>', 'TECHCETERA', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'techcetera-en', '', '', '2017-05-10 19:54:00', '2017-05-10 19:54:00', '', 0, 'http://172.16.7.177/reddesignsystems/?p=731', 0, 'post', '', 0),
