(735, 1, '2017-05-10 20:05:42', '2017-05-10 20:05:42', 'Design, planning and development of an efficient solution for VSS (client), which is responsible for the management of congestion and control of large volume of users in a certain time slot, within the physical facilities of customer service.\r\n\r\nThe system can be defined as: a flow manager or bottlenecks that allocates the means by means of a mobile application, connecting the system of allocation of entities providing public and / or private services. Guaranteeing to the user, a turn of attention without having to approach the premises physically and knowing in advance the length of time in which it will be attended.\r\n\r\n\"SIN FILAS APP\" does not eliminate the procedures established by the entities, but eliminates the rows, saves time to the user and generates the physical decongestion in the offices.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class=\"videoResponsive\"><iframe src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/ndqlM-8VhuI\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"></iframe></div>\r\n&nbsp;', 'SINFILAS', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'sinfilas-en', '', '', '2017-05-10 20:10:20', '2017-05-10 20:10:20', '', 0, 'http://172.16.7.177/reddesignsystems/?p=735', 0, 'post', '', 0),
