(742, 1, '2017-05-10 20:17:37', '2017-05-10 20:17:37', '<strong>Implementation of BPO Services</strong>\r\nThis development is an example of our ability as a BPO outsourcing company and implementing business processes. This outsourcing service requires the development of a monitoring platform, to evaluate the client service in detail in each sales outlet and each responsible person, together with a training process.\r\n\r\nThe BPO PPSyV CentAm &amp; DomRep solution was built to apply an evaluation model to customer service, where all the processes are implemented according to the methodology and specifications of the model, tailored to the needs and conditions of the market ecosystem of the company.\r\n\r\nContact us to learn more about our support for outsourcing services in companies.', 'PASIÓN POR SERVIR Y VENDER', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'pasion-por-servir-y-vender-en', '', '', '2017-05-10 20:20:23', '2017-05-10 20:20:23', '', 0, 'http://172.16.7.177/reddesignsystems/?p=742', 0, 'post', '', 0),
