(744, 1, '2017-05-10 20:22:23', '2017-05-10 20:22:23', '<strong>Role Based Training System RBC</strong>\r\nThis tailored Web application was built as a platform for training and updating processes for salespersons. A total of four versions were developed for the company, indicating the most suitable way to train staff about Oracle´s solutions and products.\r\n\r\n<strong>Revenue Tracking System</strong>\r\nWeb application built to order for a tracking system for contract renewals and expirations, contacts, alert notifications, and detailed specifications built to measure.\r\n\r\n<strong>Oracle TDT</strong>\r\nWeb application that manages budgets invested in individual and group training. This is a web development designed as a monitoring platform tailored according to customer needs.\r\n\r\n<strong>Weekly Opportunity Tracking Systems WOTS</strong>\r\nWeb development for the tracking of detailed information about business opportunities discovered at an internal level and an integrated management of numerous work teams, integrating multiple levels in the sales cycle.\r\n\r\nAll applications are installed on Oracle\'s intranet.', 'ORACLE LATIN AMERICA', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'oracle-latin-america', '', '', '2017-05-10 20:24:25', '2017-05-10 20:24:25', '', 0, 'http://172.16.7.177/reddesignsystems/?p=744', 0, 'post', '', 0),
