(750, 1, '2017-05-10 20:29:59', '2017-05-10 20:29:59', 'The Virtual Concierge is a comprehensive web development that seeks to create a more engaging experience for the guest, improving efficiency and access to information in the hotel. The system provides all the relevant information to help guests according to the location, their tastes and interests.\r\n\r\nThis application for desktops, shows information about tourism sites and entertainment, location, services and products, booking conditions, room rates, availability and comments from other guests through a web interface. All this it offered through a fun to use touch screen interaction and with a very attractive visual impact.\r\n\r\nThis web solution is structured with a Touch Screen system and software that optimizes business management and booking processes, increasing the quality of their services through a more attractive loyalty tool, and planning of the hotel resources.\r\n\r\nThe application was installed in the lobby of <a href=\"http://www.hotelesb3.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Hotel Bogota B3</a> (not available online).', 'HOTEL VIRREY', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'hotel-virrey-en', '', '', '2017-05-10 20:30:11', '2017-05-10 20:30:11', '', 0, 'http://172.16.7.177/reddesignsystems/?p=750', 0, 'post', '', 0),
