(756, 1, '2017-05-10 20:36:12', '2017-05-10 20:36:12', 'Centro de Investigaciones y Desarrollo Científico (Centre for Scientific Research and Development)\r\n\r\n<strong>Graphic Design and Corporate Image</strong>\r\nThe main objective of the Research Center´s project was the renewal of its corporate image, retaining the philosophy of CIDC and its institutional colors. The logo was modernized and standardized through a corporate image management manual in which the use of the logo, its symbolism, and the corresponding font for institutional communications were defined.\r\n\r\n<strong>Web Development for CIDC investigation center of the Universidad Central (university)</strong>\r\nWe also designed and developed a new interface for their web site, following a minimalist design guideline without needing to change its CMS platform (content management system). We created a flexible, efficient and impactful communication channel for the institution.\r\n<a href=\"http://cidc.udistrital.edu.co/web/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Link</a>', 'CENTRE FOR SCIENTIFIC RESEARCH AND DEVELOPMENT', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'centre-for-scientific-research-and-development', '', '', '2017-05-10 20:38:54', '2017-05-10 20:38:54', '', 0, 'http://172.16.7.177/reddesignsystems/?p=756', 0, 'post', '', 0),
