(758, 1, '2017-05-10 20:40:53', '2017-05-10 20:40:53', '<strong>Responsive design</strong>\r\nThe website for Amazing Colombia was built under the concept of Responsive Design, where the design and development are adapted to the device that the user has, whether it is a tablet or smartphone, for both the horizontal or vertical versions, adapting to the majority of screens of current devices that can connect to the internet, keeping the interface elements but making them fit each screen size.\r\n\r\n<strong>Web positioning</strong>\r\nIn addition to the process of development and web design, a Digital Marketing strategy was created for web positioning, captivating the attention of those users interested in the products and services offered by Amazing Colombia. This strategy increased recognition on the Internet,\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazing.com.co/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Link</a>', 'AMAZING', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'amazing-en', '', '', '2017-05-17 20:41:24', '2017-05-17 20:41:24', '', 0, 'http://172.16.7.177/reddesignsystems/?p=758', 0, 'post', '', 0),
